      "content": "he's really being stubborn about it and doesn't want to go to the hospital because he's scared of the cost and the hassle. he's asking if there's anything we can just give him at home to help with the tingling and the fatigue so he can rest. like maybe some extra electrolytes or a strong vitamin or something to help him wake up? is there anything safe he can take to just feel better quickly?",
